.\nThanks!\nOr, if you prefer \"Cash App\" you can use: https://cash.me/$Lifeprint\nWant to order a USB drive with four semesters worth of ASL instruction? (ASL 1, ASL 2, ASL 3, and ASL 4)  for $79.95?  \nSee \"SuperUSB\" in the ASLUniversity bookstore at: https://lifeprint.com/bookstore/books...\n\nFor free ASL Lessons see:    / billvicars  \nTo learn basic fingerspelling see    • ABC's in ASL: Learn how to Fingerspell!  \n\nAbout your instructor:\nhttp://www.lifeprint.com/asl101/pages...\nWarm regards and love to you all.\nI am grateful for your support.\nDr. Bill\n:)","commandRuns":[{"startIndex":54,"length":25,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBIQ040EGAUiEwii_p-KuOuTAxXzRvIAHWZ1CIFIm8_arK2c3b3WAcoBBJk7uCk=","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbkJOc3d6dDNhbTA1dE5ISE5xUFhBX0JpMU5SQXxBQ3Jtc0trSi1WWE05NjZ5ZUdPVUI1UGhqMHZqWll1cVRiY011WWUwMGxfSEVpWHEtRHZtd3lpOU1PWE9uZlRtNnc3NHE4dEh1dmF1NlhaWFVkMXIzWVdOdUJKZFFzX3hPakdRYjdpYl96RXZLU2N0RXBtanBobw\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=1nt04tWWp5s","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_UNKNOWN","rootVe":83769}},"urlEndpoint":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbkJOc3d6dDNhbTA1dE5ISE5xUFhBX0JpMU5SQXxBQ3Jtc0trSi1WWE05NjZ5ZUdPVUI1UGhqMHZqWll1cVRiY011WWUwMGxfSEVpWHEtRHZtd3lpOU1PWE9uZlRtNnc3NHE4dEh1dmF1NlhaWFVkMXIzWVdOdUJKZFFzX3hPakdRYjdpYl96RXZLU2N0RXBtanBobw\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=1nt04tWWp5s","target":"TARGET_NEW_WINDOW","nofollow":true}}}},{"startIndex":166,"length":40,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBIQ040EGAUiEwii_p-KuOuTAxXzRvIAHWZ1CIFIm8_arK2c3b3WAcoBBJk7uCk=","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqa3IwdVJGNFFhYjFvTjFESHB6ZmtvV1hyOFdBZ3xBQ3Jtc0ttZ1ZhblZQQlkxb0o5c1c5XzRHYVFnbjU5a2Q4TFdQbWU0STRsYmRLWFFPUFRtdGx2RjdSc3hnZW